WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.000
I miss this kind of life, come on

2
00:00:05.333 --> 00:00:06.866
Hey Nian Nian

3
00:00:06.966 --> 00:00:08.200
Don't be angry, okay?

4
00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:09.366
You know.

5
00:00:09.466 --> 00:00:11.900
I only like you. I don't know.

6
00:00:14.300 --> 00:00:16.933
Mom is still mad at Dad

7
00:00:16.933 --> 00:00:18.500
I heard from Xiaopang today

8
00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:20.900
The old oligarch in the village has a daughter-in-law

9
00:00:20.900 --> 00:00:22.600
It's just that two people always quarrel

10
00:00:22.600 --> 00:00:24.700
The old oligarch pissed off his wife

11
00:00:24.700 --> 00:00:26.633
No more wife

12
00:00:26.666 --> 00:00:29.300
You said dad always makes mom angry

13
00:00:29.300 --> 00:00:31.666
Will we be without a mother?

14
00:00:31.666 --> 00:00:34.100
No, I don't want mom to go

15
00:00:34.200 --> 00:00:36.333
No mom won't go

16
00:00:36.333 --> 00:00:38.200
It's all my fault for being so healthy

17
00:00:38.200 --> 00:00:39.766
If I get sick at random

18
00:00:39.766 --> 00:00:42.233
Mom won't leave no matter how angry she is

19
00:00:43.466 --> 00:00:44.733
Don't worry about it.

20
00:00:44.733 --> 00:00:46.500
Who says there is no way?

21
00:00:46.500 --> 00:00:48.533
Tingting, oops, slow down.

22
00:00:48.533 --> 00:00:50.266
I can hardly catch up with you.

23
00:00:50.266 --> 00:00:51.333
What are you doing slowly?

24
00:00:51.333 --> 00:00:53.366
Are you waiting to see that missing face?

25
00:00:53.366 --> 00:00:56.000
Tingting misses your sister-in-law

26
00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:57.566
What if you're not happy?

27
00:00:57.566 --> 00:00:59.700
It's better to make yourself feel better

28
00:01:00.166 --> 00:01:01.200
To please him

29
00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:04.066
To please him he hit my brother-in-law

30
00:01:04.066 --> 00:01:06.133
Sent the Li family and my mother-in-law to prison again

31
00:01:06.133 --> 00:01:07.400
I can't wait to beat him.

32
00:01:07.400 --> 00:01:09.066
I will go to please him

33
00:01:10.400 --> 00:01:13.166
Tingting, you are wronged.

34
00:01:13.166 --> 00:01:16.633
Sister Yu, if you marry my brother

35
00:01:16.666 --> 00:01:18.233
Will you be good to me?

36
00:01:18.966 --> 00:01:20.066
Silly girl

37
00:01:20.166 --> 00:01:22.866
I'll be nice to you even if I don't marry your brother

38
00:01:22.866 --> 00:01:25.566
In my heart, you have always been my sister.

39
00:01:25.733 --> 00:01:28.066
You are so kind

40
00:01:28.066 --> 00:01:30.833
Only someone like you deserves to marry my brother

41
00:01:30.866 --> 00:01:31.766
No way.

42
00:01:31.766 --> 00:01:34.466
I must find a way to drive that missing away

